        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The length of the inter axle prop shaft installed between the forward rear and the rear rear
                    tandem axles may be too long and could result in premature axle bearing failure. To remedy this, new
                    inter axle prop shafts will be installed.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
