            <para>
                <emph type="bold">NOTE: To determine the correct inter axle prop shaft and bearing strap kit service
                    part numbers to use, identify the suspension code and prop shaft code from the line set ticket for
                    the vehicle being serviced. Use the suspension code and prop shaft code to select the correct
                    service part numbers from Table 1.
                </emph>
            </para>
